#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.23"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.23:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.23:0.2"
msgid "3. Puggalavagga "
msgstr "3. Persons "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.23:0.3"
msgid "23. Saṅkhārasutta "
msgstr "23. Choices "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.23:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“These three people are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an3.23:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: sabyābajjhaṃ → sabyāpajjhaṃ (sabbattha)
msgctxt "an3.23:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo sabyābajjhaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, sabyābajjhaṃ vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, sabyābajjhaṃ manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti. "
msgstr "Firstly, a certain person makes hurtful choices by way of body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "an3.23:1.4"
msgid "So sabyābajjhaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, sabyābajjhaṃ vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, sabyābajjhaṃ manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā sabyābajjhaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "Having made these choices, they’re reborn in a hurtful world, "

msgctxt "an3.23:1.5"
msgid "Tamenaṃ sabyābajjhaṃ lokaṃ upapannaṃ samānaṃ sabyābajjhā phassā phusanti. "
msgstr "where hurtful contacts touch them. "

msgctxt "an3.23:1.6"
msgid "So sabyābajjhehi phassehi phuṭṭho samāno sabyābajjhaṃ vedanaṃ vedayati ekantadukkhaṃ, seyyathāpi sattā nerayikā. "
msgstr "Touched by hurtful contacts, they experience hurtful feelings that are exclusively painful—like the beings in hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.23:2.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo abyābajjhaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, abyābajjhaṃ vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, abyābajjhaṃ manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, another person makes pleasing choices by way of body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "an3.23:2.2"
msgid "So abyābajjhaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, abyābajjhaṃ vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, abyābajjhaṃ manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā abyābajjhaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "Having made these choices, they are reborn in a pleasing world, "

msgctxt "an3.23:2.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ abyābajjhaṃ lokaṃ upapannaṃ samānaṃ abyābajjhā phassā phusanti. "
msgstr "where pleasing contacts touch them. "

msgctxt "an3.23:2.4"
msgid "So abyābajjhehi phassehi phuṭṭho samāno abyābajjhaṃ vedanaṃ vedayati ekantasukhaṃ, seyyathāpi devā subhakiṇhā. "
msgstr "Touched by pleasing contacts, they experience pleasing feelings that are exclusively happy—like the gods replete with glory. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.123, sc3
msgctxt "an3.23:3.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, another person makes both hurtful and pleasing choices by way of body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "an3.23:3.2"
msgid "So sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi lokaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "Having made these choices, they are reborn in a world that is both hurtful and pleasing, "

msgctxt "an3.23:3.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi lokaṃ upapannaṃ samānaṃ sabyābajjhāpi abyābajjhāpi phassā phusanti. "
msgstr "where hurtful and pleasing contacts touch them. "

msgctxt "an3.23:3.4"
msgid "So sabyābajjhehipi abyābajjhehipi phassehi phuṭṭho samāno sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi vedanaṃ vedayati vokiṇṇasukhadukkhaṃ, seyyathāpi manussā ekacce ca devā ekacce ca vinipātikā. "
msgstr "Touched by both hurtful and pleasing contacts, they experience both hurtful and pleasing feelings that are a mixture of pleasure and pain—like humans, some gods, and some beings in the underworld. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.23:3.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti. "
msgstr "These are the three people found in the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.23:3.6"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
